{"tid":1459830,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"宜家對面既文宣係懷柔扮中立","createTime":"2019-08-12T22:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:08:22.000Z","uid":192517,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b9bcb8771d31d272b79e59f9d40ad82fc6601cf2","tid":1459830,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:20:11.000Z","msg":"而家成日都喺FB呀line呀見到呢類文<br />\n呢種文通常係好長既<br />\n分兩部份<br />\n<br />\n第一部分<br />\n強調自己香港土生土長，係咁話明白示威者既訴求原因，舉一下例子讚示威者反對得好，仲有話對示威者受傷感到痛心乜乜柒柒，總之要令讀者放下戒心，觀感良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就嚟料<br />\n喺文章好後面先會舉啲冇事實跟據既野嚟屈示威者，唔屈都會話示威者點樣「過分左」影響佢哋民生，又或者話示威者今次於理不合幫狗「澄清」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n配合洗讚好/正皮，下面洗comments話「真係中立持平」等等，製造呢啲扮中立文受到廣泛認同既假象<br />\n<br />\n雖然聽落有啲蠢，我知道好多人唔會中計，但佢哋既文宣對象係淺黃淺藍比較少留意新聞既人，少啲獨立思考都會中計<br />\n<br />\n多一兩個中計俾對家彈藥都唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957b3bd44cdedc2fdabf028cfbf9bd8d5675c4e3","tid":1459830,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:43:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebc1a9cf7fe2da5c2a8c77be51490756c739c28","tid":1459830,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:44:41.000Z","msg":"都係個d本是同根生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a0901f1d97914311f837030c4ab7c604505e72","tid":1459830,"uid":223385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"dllm，打盲完人當無事扮懷柔"},{"pid":"887c2824c4843e95de13abc33b2ac6068631c6ec","tid":1459830,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:12:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e72de65aa93fd74f9cac272e5820aa1088e517","tid":1459830,"uid":222238,"like":1